title: 'Quality product at a reasonable price.'
body: My requirements are met. I have used two of these and felt much comfortable with these socks. Good formal socks. I didn't feel I am wearing an interior quality product. Much better than the locally available socks in big bazaar and other stores. I have used Allen solley, van Heusen, jockey etc, I can't say it is in par with those brands, which are around minimum 130 per pair, but at this price point I am satisfied without compromising on quality as well. I have washed it once. Sure a decent quality socks at a reasonable price. I bought 5 pairs for 299.
